rocoite09.jpg|92px|Crocoite]]<ref name=TAS>{{cite web| url= http://www.parliament.tas.gov.au/tpl/InfoSheets/StateEmblems.htm | title= Emblems of Tasmania| author= Tasmanian Parliamentary Library website|accessdate=18 March 2018}}</ref>||-\n| -\n|-\n||'''[[Victoria (Australia)|Victoria]]'''<br>[[File:Flag of Victoria (Australia).svg|92px|Victoria]]||[[Coat of arms of Victoria (Australia)|Coat of arms of Victoria]]<br>[[File:Coat of Arms of Victoria.svg|92px]]||Badge of Victoria<br>[[File:Badge of Victoria (modern).svg|70px]]||[[Epacris impressa|Common (pink) heath]]<br>[[File:Epacris Hybrids Diadem BotGardBln1105InflorescencesZ.jpg|92px|Common (pink) heath]]||[[Helmeted honeyeater]]<br>[[File:Lichenostomus melanops - Glen Davis.jpg|92px|Helmeted honeyeater]]||[[Leadbeater's possum]]<br>[[File:Leadbeater's Possum 01 Pengo.jpg|92px|Leadbeater's possum]]||[[Weedy sea dragon|Weedy seadragon]]<br>[[File:Phyllopteryx taeniolatus1.jpg|92px|Weedy seadragon]]||'''Peace and Prosperity'''||Navy blue and white <br>\n{{colorstrip|w=3|h=4|navy|white|border=2|border-color=navy}} \n|[[Gold]]<br>[[File:Replica of Welcome Nugget at Museums Victoria.jpg|92px|Replica of Welcome Nugget at Museums Victoria]]\n| -\n|Victorian State Tartan\n|-\n||'''[[Western Australia]]'''<br>[[File:Flag of Western Australia.svg|92px|Western Australia]]||[[Coat of arms of Western Australia]]<br>[[File:Western Australian Coat of Arms.svg|92px|Coat of arms of Western Australia]]||Badge of Western Australia<br>[[File:Badge of Western Australia.svg|92px]]||[[Anigozanthos manglesii|Red and green kangaroo paw]]<br>[[File:Anigozanthos manglesii Kings Park.JPG|92px|Red and green kangaroo paw]]|||[[Black swan]]<br>[[File:Black Swans.jpg|92px|Black swan]]||[[Numbat]]<br>[[File:Numbat.jpg|92px|Numbat]]||[[Whale shark]]<br>[[File:Similan Dive Center - great whale shark.jpg|92px|center|Whale shark]]||''The Wildflower State <br> The Golden State''\n|Gold and black <br>{{colorstrip|w=3|h=4|gold|black}}\n||-||[[Gogonasus|